---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About | Project Aether">
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 w-96 h-96 bg-indigo-200/50 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-70 animate-blob"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-200/50 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-70 animate-blob animation-delay-2000"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-24 left-1/2 w-96 h-96 bg-pink-100/50 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-70 animate-blob animation-delay-4000"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-indigo-50 border border-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-8">
        <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
          <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-indigo-400 opacity-75"></span>
          <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-indigo-500"></span>
        </span>
        About Our Team
      </span>

      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-6">
        The Last Minuters
      </h1>

      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-10">
        We’re a student team focused on practical, low-cost infrastructure solutions.
        Our 2026 project works with Rand Water to address vandalism affecting water meters.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-24">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 italic">The Challenge</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Rand Water identified a rising vandalism problem: water meters are being stolen
          because their metal components have resale value. This causes service disruptions,
          repair costs, and unreliable readings.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100">
            <div class="bg-indigo-600 text-white p-2 rounded-lg mt-1">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold">Vandalism & Theft</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Meter components are targeted due to metal resale value.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-blue-500 rounded-3xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-50 transition duration-1000"></div>
        <div class="relative h-80 bg-slate-100 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
          <span class="text-slate-400 font-medium">[Field Research Image]</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-slate-50 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12">Our Solution</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-10">
        We reduce theft incentives by replacing metal parts in water meters with
        durable, non-valuable alternatives. This makes meters less attractive to steal
        while maintaining reliability and performance.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-left">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Lower Theft Value</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Remove or replace metal parts that are resold.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Reliable Hardware</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Maintain durability and measurement accuracy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Scalable Fix</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Applicable across meter types with minimal changes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
---
